<h2 id="满屏幕代码的数字雨cmatrix">满屏幕代码的“数字雨”：cmatrix</h2>
<div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>$ sudo apt-get update
$ sudo apt-get install cmatrix
$ cmatrix
</code></pre></div></div>
